**Attractive salary + super + employee benefits!**

**Your new company:**\
\
MacKellar is the mining services contractor for Bravus' Carmichael Mine.
Together, we're creating long-term jobs and meaningful opportunities
across regional Queensland.\
\
Our primary recruitment hubs are **Townsville and Rockhampton**, however
we strongly encourage applications from candidates based in **all
regional Queensland communities**.\
\
**Why MacKellar:**

-   Competitive salary with a **7/7 day/night roster** to support
    work--life balance

-   **Paid flights** direct to site from Townsville or Rockhampton

-   **Permanent role** with a long-life project and job security

-   **Meals, camp accommodation**, PPE provided, including on-site gym
    facilities and wet mess

-   At MacKellar, our core values are **Integrity, Caring, Respect and
    Courage**. We take pride in our people, our safety culture, and the
    way we work together.

**Your new role:**\
\
Join our on-site Maintenance team in a permanent position, working
a **7/7 day/night roster**. In this leadership role, you will be
responsible for coordinating safe, efficient, and cost-effective
maintenance operations.\
Key responsibilities include:

-   Leading by example to ensure maintenance activities are completed
    safely and effectively

-   Coordinating maintenance and repairs in line with safety, time, and
    budget requirements

-   Completing accurate maintenance documentation, reporting, and daily
    activity records

-   Building and maintaining strong working relationships and
    high-performing teams

-   Driving continuous improvement initiatives and implementing
    practical solutions

-   Promoting and maintaining a strong, positive safety culture across
    the team

**What you'll need to succeed:**

-   Trade qualification in **Diesel Fitting** or equivalent

-   Previous experience as a **Maintenance Supervisor** on a mine site

-   Proven track record of maintaining strong safety performance within
    teams

-   Current **Mining Supervisor -- G1, G8, G9** (formerly S1, S2, S3)

-   Current **Carry out the Risk Management Process -- G2** (RIIRIS402D)

-   Current **Queensland Coal Board Medical** (or willingness to obtain)

-   Current **Standard 11** (or willingness to obtain)

-   Current **Queensland Driver Licence**

If you are an experienced Maintenance Supervisor with a strong work
ethic, a proactive attitude, and a safety-first mindset, we'd love to
hear from you.\
Please note: only applicants with the relevant experience and
qualifications will be contacted.\
\
MacKellar is committed to providing equal employment opportunities and
embracing diversity. We encourage applications from candidates of all
backgrounds.
